      "repair_reason": "No automated repair is needed from this review; the remaining action is normal maintainer review, CI verification, and landing judgment.; Cleared: The diff changes heartbeat runtime logic, doctor diagnostics, docs, tests, and generated config hashes; I found no concrete security or supply-chain regression. (sha=3d833f9cd9b31359c6bf1a3a32982e72b8c439a7)",
